title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Nissan Navara 2015-on NP300 2.3L ST YS23 DOHC – Donaldson Pre Filter Fuel Separator Dual Bracket Kit OS-17-FSB

content.rendered:
Donaldson Fuel Water Separator Kit + Provent Bracket
Nissan Navara 2.3L ST NP300 (2015 on)
D23 YS23 DOHC Di 16V

**THIS KIT Incl. Prov/Sep Bracket !!
Can be mounted with Provent Kit OS-PROV-17 Kit >

This kit includes a bracket which will allow the fitting of both a Separator and a Provent Catch Can. Utilising one bracket for two very important uses and protecting your vehicle ! This Fuel Water Separator kit will not cause flow restriction as it is capable of 114 lph of fuel flow.

Contaminated fuel can lead to vehicle downtime and costly repairs, especially to expensive common rail systems and components. Modern engines are increasingly requiring better fuel fiLation technology to ensure delivery of the cleanest fuel to your vehicle’s fuel system.

Kit OS-PROV-17-FSB includes:
1x NAV NP300 Stainless Dual Bracket
to suit fitting ProVent 200 with Fuel Separator
1x Head Assembly
1x Donaldson Fuel Filter, Water Separator Spin-on
1x Bowl – Twist and Drain
1x rubber hose
2x Brass 90 Degrees Fittings
2x Plastic 90 Degrees Fittings
2x QuickFit Brass Fittings
2x Nuts & Bolts
1x Tube of Thread Sealant
2x Clamps

Filter Element Specifications:
Efficiency: ß11= 100 (99% @ 11 micron)
Water Separation Properties

Download PDF Installation Instructions >
